### Submit to Logic App (or Service Bus HTTP REST)
POST {{logicAppUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeName": "Bob Jones",
  "employeeEmail": "bob@company.com",
  "amount": 299.99,
  "category": "travel",
  "description": "Flight to Toronto",
  "managerEmail": "manager@company.com"
}
